| `search_icons(query="hieroglyph")` → 0 results | Fell back through `museum,artifact` → `image` → `image-01` | Full 2-level fallback chain executed |
| All icons validated | Cross-checked against `list_icons` master list | Per spec: validate each found icon against list_icons result |

